McChunk
Minecraft chunk deleter
Copyright 2011 Michael Barriault

Features:
-Renders top-down 2D render of a world
-Click-to-select chunks

Upcoming features:
-Scaled rendering for large worlds
-Easy multiple chunk selection
-Click-to-select regions
-Delete chunks
-Rearrange chunks

Known issues:
-Will almost definitely crash on large worlds.
-Some chunks aren't read correctly and won't render (doesn't seem to affect other chunks).
-Though more chunks are being read than before!
-Memory leaks very likely.
-Debug info is abundent, will clog up your Console.

Howto:
-Open app
-File->Open
-Choose folder containing .mcr files.